---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now"
  description="What I'm currently focused on and working on right now."
>
  <article class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Now</h1>

    <p class="text-lg mb-8">
      What I'm currently focused on. Inspired by{" "}
      <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        nownownow.com
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Working On</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        Building tools for structured LLM outputs in PHP with{" "}
        <a href="https://github.com/adrienbrault/instructrice">Instructrice</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        Exploring practical applications of AI agents for developer productivity
      </li>
      <li>
        This personal site - sharing learnings and building in public
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Learning</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        Latest advancements in LLM reasoning and tool use
      </li>
      <li>
        Edge computing patterns with Cloudflare Workers
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Reading</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        Technical papers on LLM architectures and training
      </li>
      <li>
        Engineering blogs from companies solving interesting problems
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Location</h2>
    <p>
      Based in France, working remotely.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] italic">
      Last updated: January 2026
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
